item.title: i think i am allergic to my shirt.
item.description: my shirt is causing my neck to turn red. usually this isn’t a good thing. but today it is awesome. !!! i got up so early today. it is weird to be up so damn early. nobody is out and around - but somehow I still managed to come to work barely by nine. I don’t quite understand how this works. I leave my house anywhere from 8-8:30ish and get here everyday at nine.
